{"tid":1118250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[暗黑料理] 出前一丁水蛋 點睇","createTime":"2019-04-21T09:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T21:08:00.000Z","uid":84786,"like":5,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"54a3659b36257e82561de987b924da3c6bd7fed9","tid":1118250,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"事先將雞蛋, 湯粉攪勻<br />\n煮好麵餅之後 放落湯碗撈勻<br />\n即刻再加落滾緊嘅熱水到湯碗一半高<br />\n(連續將滾麵同滾水撈落蛋漿係要接近100度高溫將蛋漿加熱殺菌)<br />\n等1分鐘之後食麵<br />\n<br />\n食完將個碗連蛋湯撈勻再放入微波爐叮分半鐘<br />\n出前一丁水蛋 完成!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d273ff007c26d27d08a111bf9d83b706ce5302","tid":1118250,"uid":196924,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d856222f535abd3dd61f6d98b6dcd38d41dc24","tid":1118250,"uid":38904,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"60d273ff007c26d27d08a111bf9d83b706ce5302","tid":1118250,"uid":196924,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"匡智冇教<br />\n唔好怪樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfbd974ca5c0f9d2c0f070a17d4c44649a24001","tid":1118250,"uid":18638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"食完要洗腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12c8fc42f674752fd6b134e175c59f67de6a83b","tid":1118250,"uid":84786,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"7cfbd974ca5c0f9d2c0f070a17d4c44649a24